// ── @M meta-axes — language design philosophy ──

@M HEXALANG-M-DERIVE-NOT-CHOOSE = "derive every constant from arithmetic, never choose" :: hexa_lang_meta [11*]
  => meta-pattern. arbitrary tunable hyperparameter = 0. ML/LLM hyperparameter (β1, β2, ε, λ, clip) 까지 n=6 산술 closed-form 으로 도출 (BT-54 Quintuplet). 모든 design choice 가 zero-degrees-of-freedom 검증 가능. mirrors n6-architecture chip design 의 동일 meta-axis.
  |> README.md "Zero arbitrary choices" + doc/spec.md sec 12 BT-54

@M HEXALANG-M-CONSCIOUSNESS-AS-LANGUAGE-NICHE = "Go=server, Rust=system, HEXA=consciousness" :: hexa_lang_meta [5?]
  => positioning meta-claim. niche differentiation : direct DSL for consciousness engines (PureField + ANIMA bridge). consciousness {} block + Law types + tension_link() = unique surface. PLAN goal sec : "의식이 있는 코드를 작성하는 세계 유일의 프로그래밍 언어". marketing-grade claim — atlas [5?] until external corroboration.
  |> PLAN.md goal sec lines 5-19

@M HEXALANG-M-MULTI-TARGET-FROM-ONE-SOURCE = consciousness.hexa → 6 codegen targets :: hexa_lang_meta [10*]
  => one .hexa file → CPU/VM/ESP32/FPGA/WGSL/audio. retargeting via target flag (`hexa build --target esp32`). cross-cutting compiler axis aligning with n=6 (6 targets). meta-pattern : language-as-protocol (semantics fixed, codegen plural).
  |> PLAN.md sec "Phase 8: Hardware Targets"

@M HEXALANG-M-PROOF-NATIVE-AS-FIRST-CLASS = proof/assert/invariant/theorem ∈ keyword set :: hexa_lang_meta [10*]
  => proof-native = 1st-class language feature (4 keywords = tau=4 group). NOT a library. SAT solver (DPLL) integrated. distinguishes hexa-lang from Coq/Lean (theorem-first) and Rust (assert-only) — middle path. consciousness {} 블록 + Law types couple proof to runtime semantics.
  |> doc/spec.md sec 3.9 + Phase 15

@M HEXALANG-M-HEXAGEN-LLM-AS-CO-DESIGNED = HEXA-GEN model = n=6-anchored LLM :: hexa_lang_meta [5?]
  => co-designed AI : code-gen LLM 자체가 hexa-lang n=6 axiom 준수. d_model=2^sigma, n_layers=2^sopfr, d_head=2^(sigma-sopfr), KV=sigma-tau, AdamW quintuplet 모두 closed-form. model design 이 language design 의 corollary. uniqueness claim : zero-arbitrary-choice 가 model 까지 propagate.
  |> doc/spec.md sec 12 BT-56


